videos.description: Savion Flagg cuts to the bucket and banks in a two-handed shot while absorbing the foul.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Flagg with old school 3-point play

videos.description: Savion Flagg scores the first 10 points of the game for A&M, including a 3-pointer in transition.
videos.headline: Texas AM's Flagg swishes 3-pointer in transition

videos.description: A&M's Robert Williams weak side help comes and denies the Bulls' Wes Clark of two at the cup.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Williams denies Buffalo's Clark at the rim

videos.description: Jay Jay Chandler drives to the lane and scores an acrobatic left-hand layup for the Aggies.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Chandler with the Eurostep layup

videos.description: Bulls' Montell McRae hits a 3-pointer on the fast break to ignite a 7-0 run.
videos.headline: Buffalo's McRae hits 3-pointer in transition

videos.description: Aggies Tyler Davis with a bounce pass to a cutting Chris Collins who scores the basket.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Davis, Collins execute backdoor cut for basket

videos.description: Duane Wilson threads the needle to Tonny Trocha-Morelos for an easy layup.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Trocha-Morelos, Wilson connect for bucket

videos.description: Nick Perkins hits a step back 3-pointer off glass to cut the Aggies lead.
videos.headline: The bank is open for Buffalo's Perkins

videos.description: Robert Williams get the loose ball and drives the length of the floor for a thunderous right-hand jam.
videos.headline: Texas A&M's Williams steal and leads to a power jam

videos.description: Duane Wilson and Savion Flagg connect for an alley-oop dunk to push the Aggies lead over Buffalo.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (A&M's Flagg powers home big dunk) 2017/12/21

videos.headline: A&M's Flagg powers home big dunk

videos.description: The Bulls' CJ Massinburg buries a 3-pointer and is fouled on the shot to cut into the Aggies lead.
videos.headline: Buffalo's Massinburg gets chance at 4-point play

videos.description: Robert Williams' blocked shot leads to a monster Tonny Trocha-Morelos jam for the Aggies.
videos.headline: A&M's Williams block ignites fast-break dunk

videos.description: Robert Williams receives the outlet pass and blows the open-court dunk.
videos.headline: Williams all alone for a missed dunk

videos.description: Jay Jay Chandler rises up and slams it home on the fast break for the Aggies.
videos.headline: A&M's Chandler skies and jams in the open court

videos.description: Jay Jay Chandler with a windmill dunk to rock the Aggies faithful.
videos.headline: Chandler dunks again with some shine on it

videos.description: Behind Duane Wilson's 23 points and 11 assists, the Aggies hold off the Bulls 89-73.
videos.headline: Wilson leads Texas A&M over Buffalo
